language Essence 1.3

given g, s, w : int(1..)
letting n be g * s

find schedule : matrix indexed by [int(1..w)] of set (size g) of set (size s) of int(1..n)

such that
    forAll w1 : int(1..w) . forAll w2 : int(w1+1..w) .
        forAll g1 in schedule[w1] . forAll g2 in schedule[w2] .
            |g1 intersect g2| <= 1
